data.description: Fabulous property w/6.13+/- fenced acres, featuring 2 custom built homes! Primary home is a 2bd 1 bath newly remodeled with hardwood floors, large sunroom and new HVAC in 2022. Guest house w/ full kitchen, LR, large BR and walk-in closet. Handicap accessible bathroom w/beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Detached two-car garage w/upstairs apartment that is currently money-producing. Outdoor entertainment area w/bar, 20x20 heated and cooled shop and a 24x24 pole barn. This property is ready for horses and/or other animals. Don't miss out on this perfect, rare, multi-family listing!
